%            Number of atoms       :   16 (   0 equality)
%            Maximal formula depth :    8 (   5 average)
%            Number of connectives :   14 (   2 ~  ;   0  |;   5  &)
%                                         (   0 <=>;   7 =>;   0 <=)
%                                         (   0 <~>;   0 ~|;   0 ~&)
%            Number of predicates  :    6 (   0 propositional; 1-4 arity)
%            Number of functors    :    6 (   2 constant; 0-2 arity)
